# Node — Tailwind CSS is rebuilt fresh in CI via npm ci + vite build (see
# .github/workflows/github-pages.yml), so package-lock.json IS committed and
# assets/css/dist/ is gitignored. The islands bundle (assets/js/dist/islands.js)
# is pre-built locally and committed because the network feature is gated off
# and CI does not rebuild it; flip features.network in _config.yml to re-enable.
